{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 58,
  "title": "第五十八章（為正）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "亓正閔閔 亓民屯屯 亓正察察 亓邦夬夬"
    },
    {
      "text": "禍 福之所倚 福 禍之所伏 孰知亓極"
    },
    {
      "text": "亓无正也 正復為奇 善復為訞"
    },
    {
      "text": "人之迷也 亓日固久矣"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以方而不割 兼而不刺 直而不紲 光而不耀"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其政教寬大，悶悶昧昧，似若不明也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "政教寬大，故民醇醇富厚，相親睦也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其政教急疾，言決於口，聽決於耳也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "政教急疾。民不聊生。故缺缺日以踈薄。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "倚，因也。夫福因禍而生，人遭禍而能悔過責己，修道行善，則禍去福來。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "禍伏匿於福中，人得福而為驕恣，則福去禍來。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "禍福更相生，誰能知其窮極時。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無，不也。謂人君不正其身，其無國也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "奇，詐也。人君不正，下雖正，復化上為詐也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 10,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "善人皆復化上為訞祥也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人君迷惑失正以來，其日已固久。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人行方正者，欲以率下，不以割截人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人廉清，欲以化民，不以傷害人也。今則不然，正己以害人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "肆，申也。聖人雖直，曲己從人，不自申也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人雖有獨見之明，當如闇昧，不以曜亂人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言善治政者，無形無名，無事無政可舉，悶悶然，卒至於大治，故曰，其政悶悶也。其民無所爭競，寬大淳淳，故曰，其民淳淳也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "立刑名，明賞罰，以檢姦偽，故曰察察也。殊類分析，民懷爭競，故曰，其民缺缺也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言誰知善治之極乎！唯無可正舉，無可形名，悶悶然而天下大化，是其極也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以正治國，則便復以奇用兵矣。故曰，正復為奇。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "立善以和萬物，則便復有妖之患也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人之迷惑失道，固久矣。不可便正善治以責。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以方導物，舍去其邪，不以方割物，所謂大方無隅。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "廉，清廉也；劌，傷也。以清廉清民，令去其邪，令去其汙，不以清廉劌傷於物也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以直導物，令去其僻，而不以直激沸於物也。所謂大直若屈也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 21
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以光鑑其所以迷，不以光照求其隱慝也，所謂明道若昧也，此皆崇本以息末，不攻而使復之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
